She walked down the hall and made it to the mess hall. She slowly 
walked to the food dispencer and got a glass of water.  She walked 
over to a chair in the corner of the room, facing the doorway.  She 
sat down and sipped her water.  She looked at the glass.  Glancing at 
the door every once in a while to see if someone was coming or not.

She tried to make herself as small as possable in the chair she was 
in and stayed very still.  She only moved to sip from her glass.
